I guess..? I never bought any life on ADCs, except maybe Rylais on Kai'sa for fun. But then again it's Kai'sa..

505 is just way too much imo.

Honestly, I feel like triumph saves my ass so many times in bot 2on2 when both ADCs eat an ignite. It gives you like 1 or 2 additional ticks to survive. Also it helps you scale better with the gold. In late probably Overheal might be better. But not the way I play Jhin.
